{"tid":955921,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係公司播椎名林檎既歌，比女同事恥笑我聽卡通歌","createTime":"2018-12-25T21:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T02:11:45.000Z","uid":8307,"like":164,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"aefb9e4dfc39921a9cab978cee2d5fbbc1aa3e62","tid":955921,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T21:34:43.000Z","msg":"我地公司平時都會播下歌<br />\n今日我就揀左隻東京事變既album黎播<br />\n播左陣隔離枱既女同事就走黎屌鳩我話：咪撚再播卡通歌啦<br />\n<br />\n咁我就話：<br />\n唔係動漫歌黎，流行曲黎<br />\n今期流行個椎名林檎，東京事變應該有聽過掛<br />\n<br />\n女同事：東京mud7 卡通片呀？要播就播啲正常人會聽既歌ok?<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就換左做kpop歌<br />\n嬲撚到我係咁做錯野，放工又唔記得打卡<br />\n明明早幾日先有人播歌布林殺手首op<br />\n個啲先係卡通歌lo好冇<br />\n嬲到我到依家都瞓唔著！"},{"pid":"e55f114c2099f9a186fbe7b682d81a20a85b6b30","tid":955921,"uid":33896,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T21:48:38.000Z","msg":"樓主垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fd55c20ea072b7e93636d1a9f33abbc85718b5","tid":955921,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e55f114c2099f9a186fbe7b682d81a20a85b6b30","tid":955921,"uid":33896,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T21:48:38.000Z","msg":"樓主垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T21:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21d67d635bda9b2f030dd35df07b27126d262ef","tid":955921,"uid":191815,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T21:57:50.000Z","msg":"渣架<br />\n一開波就播勇者王轟爆到佢地耳膜破裂"},{"pid":"3c2e1f7c703793e363276e92c81b04cdf7dfcd5b","tid":955921,"uid":8307,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d21d67d635bda9b2f030dd35df07b27126d262ef","tid":955921,"uid":191815,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T21:57:50.000Z","msg":"渣架<br />\n一開波就播勇者王轟爆到佢地耳膜破裂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T22:02:04.000Z",